      <h2>Common Questions from Warehouse Owners</h2>

      <p><strong>"Can I choose my own supplier?"</strong><br/>
      Yes. We are an independent credit company. You find the forklift or racking you like, get a quote, and we handle the payment to the supplier.</p>

      <p><strong>"What if my business is only 1 year old?"</strong><br/>
      As long as you've been operating for at least 6 months and have bank statements to show your turnover, we can usually help. We love helping young companies grow into bigger ones.</p>

      <p><strong>"Is there a penalty for early settlement?"</strong><br/>
